                        <interp inst="t18490409-909-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value=""></interp>NOT GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>.</p>
               <p>(<hi rend="italic">There were two other indictments against the prisoner for similar offences, on which no evidence was offered.</hi>)</p>
